    <!--
    SHARED MAIN MENU REFERENCE
    
    This file serves as the REFERENCE for the shared menu structure used by 
    both ExplorerWindow and ClassicWindow.
    
    IMPORTANT: DevExpress BarManager does not support ResourceDictionary-based 
    menu sharing due to command binding requirements. The menus MUST be defined 
    inline in each window's XAML.
    
    The ACTUAL sharing happens through:
      MainMenuViewModel: Contains all command implementations
      Both windows bind to {Binding MainMenu.CommandName}
    
    This file documents the canonical menu structure that should be maintained
    consistently across both windows. When updating menus, update this reference
    first, then copy to both ExplorerWindow.xaml and ClassicWindow.xaml.
    -->

